  m_text: "- Ch\xE8 Hu\u1EBF is a traditional dessert from the city of Hu\u1EBF in
    Central Vietnam.\n- It is often sold by street vendors and enjoyed as a snack
    rather than a full meal.\n- The dish has many variations using beans, jelly,
    coconut milk, lotus seeds, or tapioca.\n- Ch\xE8 Hu\u1EBF reflects the elegant
    food culture of the former imperial city. "
